name: Simple-budget
tagline: Simple budget calculator, estimates help give you a rough idea of how much you make, spend, and could save a year, month, week, day, second.
body:
### Simple Budget
Input some basic paycheck and monthly bills information and a percentage of how much you'd like to save to see how much you make, have left over, could save - per year, month, week, day, minute, second.  JS only, no information is saved, its gone on refresh.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
